				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Sprite 0 hit gets into a ~20-pixel-wide ballpark. Polling on $2004 over the next few lines allows correcting from that ballpark to an exact position plus or minus one pixel. This sort of precise alignment to the horizontal blank becomes especially important for mid-frame palette changes.<br /><br />And to Codemasters and Color Dreams, everything was undocumented.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

